@@ IMPRESSUM section — Phase 4 migration of SectionImpressum.astro
@@ Indentation is not implicit: every leading space below is typed on purpose.
@@ The German legal-text overlay is NOT modeled with @SLOT here. Unlike the
@@ old pre-rework design docs/CLAUDE.md still describe, the current
@@ SectionImpressum.astro positions that overlay as a plain sibling div,
@@ measured at runtime against specific rendered row indices via JS - not
@@ through PunchCard's slot-injection mechanism. This card is therefore
@@ just a plain 19-row DISPLAY/END-DISPLAY frame, nothing more.
@ROWS 19

@DIVISION PROCEDURE
@SECTION IMPRESSUM id=impressum

@CARD IMPRESSUM-SECTION
 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
 IMPRESSUM-SECTION.
     DISPLAY











     END-DISPLAY
* GOBACK TO PROCEDURE DIVISION LINKS SECTION
     {{link:impressum}}EXIT SECTION{{/link}}
     .
